2. Almonds
3. Honey
4. Milk
5. Yogurt
6. Sugar
7. Cinnamon
8. Semolina

10. Sesame seeds
11. Dates

13. Pomegranates
14. Saffron
15. Cardamom

19. Coconut
20. Cocoa powder
